sourcesContent: import * as React from "react"; import Stack from "@mui/material/Stack"; import Button from "@mui/material/Button"; import { Navigate } from "react-router-dom"; import { ShowProduct } from "./ShowProduct"; import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { StoreData } from "../../Redux/Action/action"; const Head = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch(); dispatch(() => { fetch("http://localhost:3002/productdata") .then((res) => res.json()) .then((res) => dispatch(StoreData(res))) .catch((err) => console.log(err)); }, []); const x = useSelector((state) => state.data); console.log(x); return ( ); }; export { Head };
